High-level difference (say this first)

send is low-level, asynchronous message passing, while GenServer.call is a high-level, synchronous requestâ€“response abstraction built on top of message passing.

1ï¸âƒ£ send(pid, message)
What it is

Primitive BEAM operation

Sends a message to a processâ€™s mailbox

Does not wait for any response

